	)
	(text "Abracon ABM8-24.000MHZ-B2T\n24Mhz divides cleanly to 48 MHz USB clock and 170 MHz system clock.\n\nCapacitance Calculation:\n\nCload_target = 18 pF and Cstray = 4 pF\nCload = (CL1 × CL2) / (CL1 + CL2) + Cstray\n(CL1 × CL2)/(CL1 + CL2) = 14 pF,\nif CL1 = CL2, each is 28 pF. \n\nSo 27 pF or 33 pF Capacitors\nMost designs end up at 18-22 pF caps for an 18 pF crystal.\n\nTune this on the bench by trying 18 pF, 22 pF, 27 pF caps."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 18.542 75.184 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(thickness 0.1588)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "818377ae-7fdc-44b5-8a1a-31b3feed0875")
	)
